      "Bash(PRE_COMMIT_ALLOW_NO_CONFIG=1 git commit -m \"$(cat <<''EOF''\nInfrastructure Spring Cleaning Complete - SQLAlchemy fixes and protocols\n\nMission Accomplished:\n- Fixed SQLAlchemy metadata cache synchronization using Chief Architect''s 3-step approach\n- Added GitHub-First Status Verification protocol to CLAUDE.md\n- Resolved database environment mismatch (local vs Docker PostgreSQL)\n- Verified PM-063 QueryRouter degradation system complete\n- Enhanced conftest.py with nuclear option cache clearing\n\nAll acceptance criteria met with comprehensive evidence validation.\n\n🤖 Generated with [Claude Code](https://claude.ai/code)\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>\nEOF\n)\")",
